0:16:49.660,0:16:53.880
Usiku, pandaienda panze, ndakanga ndisingagoni kutarisa mudenga

0:16:53.880,0:16:59.240
nokuti ndaiona nyoka nemhuka dzisingazikamwi dzichibuda kubva kudenga.

0:16:59.240,0:17:04.920
Panyama, ndaiona nyoka kumativi ose, dzichindi dzingirira.

0:17:04.920,0:17:11.620
Vanhu vakafa kare kare, vandaiziva, vakange vakandikomberedza uye mabhokisi.

0:17:11.620,0:17:16.440
Dzimwe nguva, ndainzwa mazwi asingazivikanwi, achindiudza kuti ndaizofa.

0:17:16.440,0:17:23.940
Ndakazviona ndichisundidzirwa muguva kana mugungwa.

0:17:23.940,0:17:31.240
Ndakange ndisisakwanise kuzvitakura zvakare. Saka, ndaitsvaga kununurwa kwese kwese.

0:17:31.240,0:17:37.360
Pandakanga ndava kuda kuroorwa, manheru aizotevera zuva remuchato wangu,

0:17:37.360,0:17:40.680
Ndakanzwa mazwi andisingazive achindidana.

0:17:40.680,0:17:45.240
Ndakazeza. Saka, vakatanga kukanda miseve kwandiri.

0:17:45.240,0:17:49.280
Ndakamhanya nokukurumidza kunzvimbo yekunamatira kunorara ikoko.

0:17:49.280,0:17:56.520
Yakanga iri chechi imwe cheteyo yandaienda iyo yaiva neboka rezvemweya iroro.

0:17:56.520,0:18:03.460
Iwe uri kutitaurira iye zvino kuti chechi imwecheteyo ndiyo yakatanga boka rezve mweya, handizvo here?

0:18:03.460,0:18:05.140
Hongu, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:18:05.140,0:18:08.800
Tinoda kuti uise chimwe chiedza pamusoro pekuti vakaumba sei boka revanhu vaiita zvemweya,

0:18:08.800,0:18:14.300
kuti wakawana sei kutaura uku nendimi,

0:18:14.300,0:18:16.080
kuti wakagamuchira sei mukurota,

0:18:16.080,0:18:21.060
uye pawakasangana nomufundisi, kuti mufundisi akakukurudzira sei.

0:18:21.060,0:18:28.420
Ndihwo husiku ihwohwo apo vakatinamatira kuti tigamuchire chibereko che Mweya Mutsvene.

0:18:28.420,0:18:30.840
Ndakanga ndisingagoni saka ndakasuruvara

0:18:30.840,0:18:37.580
nokuti mufundisi aitungamirira akatiudza kuti chimwe chezvipo chiri nyore kugamuchira

0:18:37.580,0:18:41.320
kubva ku Mweya Mutsvene chaiva chekutaura nendimi.

0:18:41.320,0:18:44.000
Ndakasuruvara ndokuenda kunorara.

0:18:44.000,0:18:47.500
Mukurota kwangu, ndakaona mumwe wevatungamiri.

0:18:47.500,0:18:51.820
Akandikumbira kuti nditaure mushure make muchiroto.

0:18:51.820,0:18:54.460
Asi ndakanga ndisingagoni kutaura mukurota.

0:18:54.460,0:19:00.860
Zuva rakatevera, ndakaenda kumufundisi ndokutsanangura kusangana kwandakaita mukurota kwaari.

0:19:00.860,0:19:04.540
Zvakanaka. Muchiroto ichocho, wakaona mumwe wevafundisi?

0:19:04.540,0:19:05.180
Hongu.

0:19:05.180,0:19:08.600
Uye iye akati kwauri mukurota uku kuti iwe unofanira kutaura mushure make

0:19:08.600,0:19:11.260
asi muchiroto ichocho, iwe wakatadza kutaura?

0:19:11.260,0:19:13.120
Kwete, handina kukwanisa kutaura.

0:19:13.120,0:19:15.820
Asi iwe wakamuka -

0:19:15.820,0:19:17.620
Uye ndakabvunza mutungamiriri.

0:19:17.620,0:19:18.620
Panyama?

0:19:18.620,0:19:23.060
Ehe. Akandikumbira kuti nditaure nenzira iyo mukadzi akaita.

0:19:23.060,0:19:27.380
Ndakaita; Ndakataura nendimi.

0:19:27.380,0:19:33.280
Akati, "Ndizvozvo, tanga kubva ipapo, iwe uchakura mazviri".

0:19:33.280,0:19:36.920
Zuva randakataura naye, ndimi dzacho dzaingove pfupi chete.

0:19:36.920,0:19:41.560
Gare gare, ndakaona kuti dzakazo reba chaizvo.

0:19:41.560,0:19:45.020
Handaikwanisa kudzidzivisa; chido chacho chakaramba chichiuya.

0:19:45.020,0:19:49.680
Pandaive nepamuviri, havi yacho yakawedzera.

0:19:49.680,0:19:55.300
Ndisati ndazviziva, ndakasvodza.

0:19:55.300,0:19:59.960
Wakazoziva sei kuti zvawaiita zvakanga zvisina kururama;

0:19:59.960,0:20:04.220
kutaura nendimi - idzo waitaura dzakanga dzisiri dza Mwari

0:20:04.220,0:20:07.400
asi kubva mugomba regehena? Wakaziva sei?

0:20:07.400,0:20:12.760
Ndakazviona pandakanga ndichidzingirirwa nevakadzi vandaisaziva muzviroto zvangu.

0:20:12.760,0:20:17.980
Ndakanga ndichinyengetera asi munyengetero chaiwo mumutauro wakajeka waisauya.

0:20:17.980,0:20:22.900
Pakarepo, kutaura kwangu nendimi kwakauya zvakasimba.

0:20:22.900,0:20:27.440
Vakadzi muhope dzangu vakapindura kwandiri nendimi.

0:20:27.440,0:20:29.540
Ndipo pandakatya.

0:20:29.540,0:20:34.900
Pandakaenda kumachechi, ndakanzwa vafundisi nevarwi vemunamato

0:20:34.900,0:20:38.440
vachinyengetera mumutauro mumwechetewo saka ndakatya.

0:20:38.440,0:20:41.660
Ndipo pandakaziva kuti zvaive zvekunyepa.

0:20:41.660,0:20:45.760
Kubvira vhiki yapfuura apo ini ndakaponeswa,

0:20:45.760,0:20:52.020
Handina chido chokutaura zvakare uye ndinorara zvakanaka.

0:20:52.020,0:20:53.620
Zviroto zvako zvakaita sei?

0:20:53.620,0:21:03.980
Dzimwe nguva, ndinorota ndiri muchechi ndichishanda nemi kana kuti ndiri pane imwe nzvimbo ndichidzidzisa vana.

0:21:03.980,0:21:08.700
Sei dzikinuro ichifanirwa kubvisa rurimi irworwo?

0:21:08.700,0:21:14.000
Kana ndimi idzodzo dzichibva kuna Mwari, dzikinuro inofanira kuwedzera.

