0:22:14.620,0:22:18.640
Iwe unotanga kuponeswa usati wagona kuponesa vamwe.

0:22:18.640,0:22:23.560
Kuburikidza nehuwandu hwemwoyo, muromo unotaura.

0:22:23.560,0:22:31.800
Zvaunotakura, zviri mukati mako, ndizvo zvichataura ne kupa kune vamwe.

0:22:31.800,0:22:35.840
